rth it.The service we received was faultless. Tipping is not expected; indeed the concept is not really understood. But you will really want to provide a tip 鈥?not feel obliged to give one because you feel you have to, as with some other parts of the world鈥?br/>I can鈥檛 comment on the gym and pool as we never used them. I have nothing negative to say to say about the hotel. If forced, I would say that it was a bit 鈥榙ated鈥?but I heard it was due for a facelift. But, regardless, the New Otani is Fantastic.Recommend this Hotel? DEFINITELY 
